original_title: Dagny - om jag sätter mig ner nu dör jag
overview: In 2015, Dagny Carlsson quickly garnered the attention of millions of Swedes when she started blogging for the first time at age 102. Now at age 106, wanting to experience as much as she can, she accepts an invitation from a Finnish film director who wants her to star in a short film. So, off to Åland she goes!
title: Dagny - om jag sätter mig ner nu dör jag
